# Community Parking Occupancy local rules

- Windows + PowerShell is the default environment.
- Do not use Docker for this project.
- Backend: `backend/`, Spring Boot 3, port 8087.
- Frontend: `frontend/`, Vite, port 5173.
- AI: `ai-service/`, FastAPI, conda env `python39`, port 8000.
- Database: local MySQL `smart_parking` on port 3306.
- Redis: local Redis on port 6379.
- Do not commit `.env`, logs, build outputs, `node_modules`, or model files.

Common commands:

```powershell
powershell.exe -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File .\scripts\install-local-deps.ps1
powershell.exe -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File .\scripts\start-demo-local.ps1
```
